dding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.6;text-rendering: optimizelegibility;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 28px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 19px\">3</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 19px;font-family: 宋体\">月</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 19px\">27</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 19px;font-family: 宋体\">日，中国联合网络通信有限公司茂名市分公司副总经理邓安民来到我院，为南校区的师生们带来一场真实的</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 19px\">5G</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 19px;font-family: 宋体\">演示，讲座在南校区</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 19px\">1</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 19px;font-family: 宋体\">栋</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 19px\">301</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 19px;font-family: 宋体\">教学楼举行，由计算机工程系主任周洁文主持。现场还邀请到茂名联通政企部经理张创前、茂名联通电白区分公司老总张雯静。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 1.25rem;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 1rem;line-height: 1.6;text-rendering: optimizelegibility;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-indent: 28px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 19px;font-family: 宋体\">中国联合网络通信有限公司茂名市分公司副总经理邓安民先生为我们讲解了关于</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 19px\">5G</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 19px;font-family: 宋体\">的基本技术、在行业中的应用以及现在联通</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 19px\">5G</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 19px;font-family: 宋体\">的进展程度，最后，现场还设置了答疑环节，由邓安民先生为大家解答关于</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 19px\">5G</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 19px;font-family: 宋体\">的一系列